HOCKEY RULES ICE AND INLINE HOCKEY TOUR -
NHL HOCKEY RULES ICE and INLINE HOCKEY TOUR presented
by Southwest Airlines is a series of weekend indoor
ice and inline hockey tournaments open to youth in
the 8 and under through 17 and under categories. The
tour visits 19 NHL cities throughout the NHL season.
